<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Loath" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Loath,</orth> (comp. <cit><quote>--er,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.355" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 355</bibl></cit>) unwilling, not liking, disinclined: <cit><quote>although I seem so l., I am the last,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.160" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 160</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>though l., yet must I be content,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.6.48" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 6, 48</bibl></cit>. Followed by an inf.: <cit><quote>that I shall be l. to do,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 2, 39</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I am very l. to be your idol,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.129" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 129</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I would be l. to turn them together,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.193" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 193</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.6.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 6, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. IV, 1, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.5.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 5, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.128" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 128.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. aww 5.3.201" default="NO" valid="yes">All's V, 3, 201</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 184</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.583" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 583</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.5.1" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 5, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.169" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 3, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.1.128" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 1, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.166" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 166</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.167" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 167</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.355" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 355</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.114" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 114</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.10" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 2, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.4.88" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.209" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 7, 209</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.2.243" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 2, 243</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.273" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 273</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.107" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.86" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 86</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.5.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 5, 13</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>